Subject:
draft on the fluorochemical study/methods and results
Body:
Geary,

We have prepared the first draft on methods/results.  Please review the
attached files.  I have decided to report the results from non-parametric
statistical analyses as the compounds.

We may need to combine some of the tables.  The figures are for your
reference - may or may not need to include them in the manuscript.

Look forward to receiving your and your colleagues' input.

Regards,
Han Yao


 - method.wpd
 - pfosgraph.wpd
